<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EC) No 2443/96 of 17 December 1996 providing for additional measures for direct support of producers' incomes or for the beef and veal sector </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) NR 2443/96, millega n&auml;hakse ette tootjate sissetulekute v&otilde;i veise- ja vasikalihaturu otsetoetuse lisameetmed </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION, </inglise>
<eesti> 17. detsember 1996 EUROOPA LIIDU N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, and in particular Articles 42 and 43 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artikleid 42 ja 43, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament (1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi arvamust ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in the light of the continuing serious difficulties in the beef and veal sector resulting from consumer concerns in relation to bovine spongiform encephalopathy (BSE) and further to those measures which were taken to support producers' incomes by Council Regulation (EC) No 1357/96 (2), additional measures for the direct support of producers' incomes or for the beef and veal sector are necessary; </inglise>
<eesti> veiste spongiaalsest entsefalopaatiast (BSE-t&otilde;vest) tingitud tarbija rahutusest tulenevate j&auml;tkuvate t&otilde;siste raskuste t&otilde;ttu veise- ja vasikalihaturul ja vastavalt n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rusele (E&Uuml;) nr 1357/96 tootjate sissetulekute toetamiseks v&otilde;etud meetmete t&auml;iendamiseks on vaja v&otilde;tta lisameetmeid tootjate sissetulekute v&otilde;i veise- ja vasikalihaturu otsetoetuse tarvis; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the amount of aid available to each Member State for direct support of producers' incomes or for the beef and veal sector will be distributed according to a key which takes into account, in particular, the size of the beef herd in each Member State; whereas it is appropriate that Member States should distribute the total amount of finance available on the basis of objective criteria, while avoiding any market distortion; </inglise>
<eesti> igale liikmesriigile k&auml;ttesaadav abi tootjate sissetulekute v&otilde;i veise- ja vasikalihaturu otsetoetuseks jagamisel v&otilde;etakse aluseks eelk&otilde;ige lihakarja suurus igas liikmesriigis; liikmesriikidel on vaja jagada kogu k&auml;ttesaadav raha objektiivsete kriteeriumide alusel, v&auml;ltides turu h&auml;ireid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for budgetary reasons, the Community will finance the expenditure incurred by Member States in relation to the direct support of producers' incomes or for the beef and veal sector only where such payments are made by a certain deadline, </inglise>
<eesti> eelarvelistel p&otilde;hjustel rahastab &uuml;hendus liikmesriikide kulutusi seoses tootjate sissetulekute v&otilde;i veise- ja vasikalihaturu otsetoetusega ainult juhul, kui maksed on tehtud teatud t&auml;htajaks, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall use the amounts set out in the Annex to make additional payments, according to objective criteria, to support producers' incomes or the beef and veal sector in their territory, provided that these payments do not cause distortion of competition. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid kasutavad lisas t&auml;psustatud summasid lisamakseteks objektiivsete kriteeriumide alusel, toetamaks tootjate sissetulekuid v&otilde;i veise- ja vasikalihaturgu, tingimusel et need maksed ei moonuta konkurentsi. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The measures introduced by Article 1 of this Regulation shall be deemed to be intervention intended to stabilize agricultural markets within the meaning of Article 3 (1) of Council Regulation (EEC) No 729/70 of 21 April 1970 on the financing of the common agricultural policy (3). </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikliga 1 kasutusele v&otilde;etud meetmeid k&auml;sitletakse p&otilde;llumajandusturu stabiliseerimiseks kavandatud sekkumisena n&otilde;ukogu 21. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 729/70 (&uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika rahastamise kohta) artikli 3 l&otilde;ikes 1 m&auml;&auml;ratletud t&auml;henduses. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The Community shall finance the expenditure incurred by Member States in relation to the payments referred to in Article 1 only where such payments are made by them by 15 October 1997 at the latest. </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;hendus rahastab liikmesriikide kulutusi seoses artiklis 1 osutatud maksetega ainult juhul, kui need maksed tehakse hiljemalt 15. oktoobriks 1997. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The conversion rate to be applied shall be the agricultural rate valid on 1 December 1996. </inglise>
<eesti> Kohaldatav &uuml;mberarvestuskurss on 1. detsembril 1996 kehtiv p&otilde;llumajanduslik &uuml;mberarvestuskurss. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> Any detailed rules necessary for the application of this Regulation shall be adopted in accordance with the procedure set out in Article 27 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 805/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in beef and veal (4). </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse vajalikud &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad v&otilde;etakse vastu koosk&otilde;las n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 805/68 (veise- ja vasikalihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta) artiklis 27 s&auml;testatud menetlusega. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub selle Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall not be applicable before the day the general budget of the European Communities for the financial year 1997 has been declared as finally adopted. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevat m&auml;&auml;rust ei rakendata enne p&auml;eva, kui Euroopa &uuml;henduste 1997. majandusaasta &uuml;ldeelarve on tunnistatud l&otilde;plikult vastuv&otilde;etuks. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
